<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Hello Max,<br/>I would recommend the abridged Chaim Rabin 2017 repress of 1952 translation.<br/><br/>The full book is quite a heavy read, the abridged version can be<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Hello Max,<br />I would recommend the abridged Chaim Rabin 2017 repress of 1952 translation.<br /><br />The full book is quite a heavy read, the abridged version can be read in two or three days at about 250 pages.<br /><br />Robin<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
